name: Blossom Box Set / Pastel
description:
Blossom Box Set / Pastel

Our blossom box set comes with 10 blossom pom poms and a length of  natural jute twine and they are perfect for any occasions !The pom poms will be shipped fully opened ( each pom pom measures 5cm across ) and has a small loops to attach onto the twine easily. 

Suggestions for use: Napkin ring, gift wrap, cake toppers, hair piece, blossom lapel.....
